com.kkyria16.crawler

Class Project

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.kkyria16.crawler.Project

  • public class Project
extends java.lang.Object
    Project This is an object declaration and structure for storing and managing Projects found at crawling phase. Here are being stores 6 basic information for each project: project name, author, stars rated, language written, licenses has and a direct project repository link from GitHub.
    Version:
    1.0.0
    Author:
    Kyriakos Kyriakou
